  "text": "Second, we develop another key predistribution scheme by combining the random subset assignment [CITATION_1] with the expected location information. This scheme offers further trade-offs between the security against node captures and the probability of establishing pairwise keys directly between neighbor nodes given a certain memory constraint. Our analysis also indicates that this scheme provides a higher probability to establish pairwise keys directly between neighbor sensor nodes and better resistance against node captures than the original scheme in [CITATION_2] .",
